            "title": "Referral for high risk breast specialty evaluation",
            "description": "Consider referral to breast specialist to discuss primary risk reduction interventions such as chemoprevention.\n\nWomen at greater risk, such as those with a genetic marker or syndrome associated with increased risk of breast cancer, may derive more benefit than harm from risk-reducing medications.",
